# postbackSequenceIndex

**Instance Property**

The position of this postback among all postbacks for an ad impression.

## Declaration

```swift
var postbackSequenceIndex: Int { get }
```

## Discussion

For more information about receiving time-delayed postbacks for an ad impression, see [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/StoreKit/receiving-postbacks-in-multiple-conversion-windows].

## Getting general information

- **version**: The SKAdNetwork version that the postback uses.
- **transactionIdentifier**: A unique transaction identifier that the system generates.
- **isRegistered**: A Boolean value that indicates whether the postback is registered in the testing environment.
- **isRedownload**: A Boolean value that indicates whether the user redownloaded and reinstalled the app.
